<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <!-- Header -->
  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- Box: Problema e introduzione potenze -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-3 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-400 rounded-3xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start gap-6 mb-6">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">&#8226;</span> Leggi e osserva.</h3>
          <div class="p-3 bg-custom-blue-light dark:bg-cyan-900/40 rounded-lg mb-3">
            <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
              Nella pasticceria di Martina vengono preparate 6 scatole con 6 confezioni di 6 cioccolatini ciascuna. Quanti cioccolatini in tutto vengono preparati?
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-3">
            Per rispondere alla domanda puoi usare la moltiplicazione.
          </p>
          <p class="font-bold mb-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            <span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400">6</span> scatole × <span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400">6</span> confezioni × <span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400">6</span> cioccolatini = <span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400">216</span> cioccolatini
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">
            Hai moltiplicato il numero <span class="font-bold">6</span> per se stesso <span class="font-bold">3</span> volte.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 italic">
            Puoi scrivere anche così: <span class="font-bold text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400">6</span> × <span class="font-bold text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400">6</span> × <span class="font-bold text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400">6</span> = <span class="font-bold text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">6³</span>, che si legge "sei alla terza" oppure "sei elevato alla terza".
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Spiegazione base ed esponente con immagine -->
      <div class="p-4 md:p-6 bg-pink-100 dark:bg-pink-900/30 rounded-lg mb-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-4 mb-3">
          <%= image_tag 'nvi5_mat/p016/p016_01.jpg', alt: 'Martina pasticciera', class: 'max-w-[150px] rounded-lg dark:bg-white dark:p-1' %>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            <p><span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">&#9654;</span> Il <span class="font-bold">6</span> si chiama <span class="font-bold">base</span> ed è il fattore che deve essere ripetuto.</p>
            <p><span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">&#9654;</span> Il <span class="font-bold">3</span> si chiama <span class="font-bold">esponente</span> e indica quante volte devi moltiplicare la base per se stessa.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
          Questa operazione si chiama <span class="font-bold">elevamento a potenza</span> e significa 6 × 6 × 6.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Potenze particolari -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-bold text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 mb-3">Potenze particolari</h2>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="font-bold text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 whitespace-nowrap">5<sup>1</sup> = 5</div>
            <span class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">→</span>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Tutti i <span class="font-bold">numeri elevati a 1</span> rimangono uguali a <span class="font-bold">se stessi</span>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="font-bold text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 whitespace-nowrap">5<sup>0</sup> = 1</div>
            <span class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">→</span>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Tranne 0, qualsiasi <span class="font-bold">numero elevato a 0</span> dà come risultato <span class="font-bold">1</span>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="font-bold text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 whitespace-nowrap">1<sup>6</sup> = 1</div>
            <span class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">→</span>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Qualsiasi <span class="font-bold">potenza di base 1</span> dà come risultato <span class="font-bold">1</span>. Infatti: 1 × 1 × 1 × 1 × 1 × 1 = 1</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="font-bold text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 whitespace-nowrap">0<sup>4</sup> = 0</div>
            <span class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">→</span>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Qualsiasi <span class="font-bold">potenza di base 0</span> dà come risultato <span class="font-bold">0</span>. Infatti: 0 × 0 × 0 × 0 = 0</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Le potenze di 10 -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 mb-4">Le potenze di 10</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4 font-semibold"><span class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">&#8226;</span> Osserva.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-1 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            <p><span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">10<sup>0</sup></span> = 1</p>
            <p><span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">10<sup>1</sup></span> = 1<span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">0</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">10<sup>2</sup></span> = 10 × 10 = 1<span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">00</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">10<sup>3</sup></span> = 10 × 10 × 10 = <span class="whitespace-nowrap">1 <span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">000</span></span></p>
            <p class="col-span-2"><span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">10<sup>4</sup></span> = 10 × 10 × 10 × 10 = <span class="whitespace-nowrap">10 <span class="text-cyan-500 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold">000</span></span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-72 self-start">
          <div class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-3 border-pink-500 dark:border-pink-400 rounded-3xl">
            <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
              Nel valore delle <span class="font-bold">potenze di 10</span>, il <span class="font-bold">numero degli zeri</span> coincide con l'<span class="font-bold">esponente</span>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sezione ESERCIZI -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 mb-6">ESERCIZI</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Exercise 1: Scrivi sotto forma di potenza -->
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(1) %>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Scrivi, quando è possibile, i seguenti numeri sotto forma di potenza.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-11">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-4">
              <%= render 'shared/fill_list',
                  color: "#{ @pagina.base_color }",
                  equals: true,
                  items: [
                    { prefix: "9 × 9 × 9", answer: "9^3" },
                    { prefix: "5 × 5", answer: "5^2" },
                    { prefix: "4 × 3 × 4", answer: "impossibile" },
                    { prefix: "10 × 10", answer: "10^2" }
                  ],
                  container_class: "contents" %>
            </div>
            <!-- Box spiegazione -->
            <div class="p-4 bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 border-2 border-yellow-300 dark:border-yellow-600 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200 mb-2">Come scrivere le potenze con il computer</h4>
              <div class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 space-y-2">
                <p>Sul computer non possiamo scrivere l'esponente in alto, quindi usiamo il simbolo <span class="font-bold text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-400">^</span></p>
                <p>Ad esempio: 5 × 5 × 5 = 5³ si scrive <span class="font-bold bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded">5^3</span></p>
                <p class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700">Se l'operazione <span class="font-bold">non è una potenza</span> (perché i fattori non sono tutti uguali), scrivi <span class="font-bold bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded">impossibile</span></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Exercise 2: Calcola le potenze -->
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
            <%= numero_esercizio_badge(2) %>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Calcola sul quaderno le seguenti potenze.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4 ml-11">
            <% [
              { pot: "4<sup>3</sup>", answer: "64" },
              { pot: "12<sup>2</sup>", answer: "144" },
              { pot: "10<sup>5</sup>", answer: "100000" },
              { pot: "18<sup>1</sup>", answer: "18" },
              { pot: "6<sup>0</sup>", answer: "1" },
              { pot: "10<sup>3</sup>", answer: "1000" }
            ].each do |item| %>
              <div class="text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
                <div class="font-bold mb-2"><%= item[:pot].html_safe %></div>
                <input type="text" data-correct-answer="<%= item[:answer] %>" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/quaderno_link', pagine: [181, 183] %>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
